<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-594-321  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 594 321.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  Nov 12 1990 v7 n44 p3(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Cahners-Ziff Publishing Associates LP 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Marc word processing division sold to tool vendor. (ProgrammedIntelligence and Marc Software International form WordmarcInternational)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Varney, Sarah E.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Programmed Intelligence Corp. (Acquisitions and mergers)MARC Software International Inc. (Acquisitions and mergers).andO;Product:   Composer+ (Word processing software) (Marketing)Intelligent Query (Report generating software) (Planning).andO;Topic:     Word ProcessingJoint VentureMarketing StrategyAcquisition.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Marc word processing division sold to tool vendorandM;Programmed Intelligence of Atlanta has acquired the word processing divisionof Marc Software International of Palo Alto, Calif.andP;  Under the agreement,Wordmac International has been created to accomodate the division.andM;Marc Software is the developer of Composer+, a word processing package forVAX/VMS, Unix and DOS platforms.andP;  Wordmarc International will be based inPalo Alto and will handle sales, support and development functions.andM;Programmed Intelligence President Rick Chitty said Composer+ is ahigh-quality product that stacks up well against other word processingpackages, but suffers less-than-adequate product support.andM;&quot;We hope to add a little marketing and sales pizzazz,&quot; Chitty said.andM;Intelligent Query, Programmed Intelligence's report writer and query tool,supports more than 50 databases.andP;  Users can access VAX data regardless ofwhere the data is, Chitty said.andP;  The program also lets non-technical usersselectively retrieve information from databases and applications.andM;Wormarc eventually will combine the word processing functions of Composer+with the data retrieval abilities of Intelligent Query, Chitty said, allowingthe creation of word processing documents with data from various databases.andM;Financial terms of the deal were not disclosed.andO;</TEXT></DOC>